				<td colspan="2"><span>My main is a 65 raiding cleric, and it does bother me when people are asking for essentially cleric nerfs. Clericking is a long, hard road, we pay for our abilities in a lot of ways, the least of which is the complete and total inability to solo. As a bard, I can solo things at 52 that my cleric would never have a chance to solo.
<br />

